Package: voice-ctrl
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, portaudio19-dev, xclip, python3-tk, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Maintainer: VoiceControl Team <support@voicecontrol.example>
Description: System-wide voice dictation for Ubuntu
 VoiceControl is a voice dictation tool that allows you to convert speech
 to text using OpenAI's Whisper API. Press a keyboard shortcut to record
 your voice, and the transcribed text will be automatically pasted at your
 cursor position.
 .
 Features:
  - Global keyboard shortcut for recording
  - OpenAI Whisper API integration
  - System tray icon with status indicator
  - Settings window for configuration
  - Transcription history viewer
  - Audio feedback (beeps)
